headline: West Monroe Appoints Accenture Veteran Harin Shetty to Role of President, Board of Directors
summary: West Monroe, a global business and technology consulting firm, today announced Harin Shetty has joined the firm as President and board member, reporting to CEO Gil Mermelstein. He will be based out of the firm's Chicago headquarters.
